outputs.output_title: PA for the Small Arms Control
outputs.output_descr: PA for Small Arms Control is is a 1-year pilot project for small arms control in Liberia. The project operation in four chiefdoms (Kissi, Quardu-Gboni, Bain-Garr and Tchien-Meayea-Kannah) in 3 counties (Lofa, Nimba and Grand Gedeh.
